    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty strong take. i mean, i get the civil war part, but some people argue that without the intervention, Gaddafi would've just carried out a massacre of his own people in Benghazi. wasn't there at least a humanitarian success there in preventing a mass killing?",
